Cmus = to play music in terminal
moc = stands for music on console altenative to cmus.to start moc type mocp in terminal
vlc and celluoid = to play video file
okular and zathura = to open any document i.e pdf,txt etc
vifm = file manager for vim
ranger = same as vifm but has preview feature for icons,images and video
screenkey = screencast tool to display keystrokes
screenfetch = shows desktop environment info in details
vlock = locks your virtual terminal session useful for security in multiuser mode
slock = screen locker 
tmux and terminator = multiple terminator in one window 
figlet =  Make large character ASCII banners out of ordinary or big
